{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 09:22:04.264575", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission accepted.\n\nSummary of submitted solution:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"pc_0_0\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"host_incorrect_ip\", \"host_incorrect_gateway\", \"host_ip_conflict\"]\n\nRecommended corrective steps (optional, brief)\n1. On pc_0_0, set the correct IP and gateway for leaf_router_0_0's subnet:\n   - Example: ip addr add 10.0.0.<X>/24 dev <iface> (choose an unused host IP in 10.0.0.0/24)\n   - ip route replace default via 10.0.0.1\n   - Or use DHCP if available on that subnet.\n\n2. Verify from leaf_router_0_0:\n   - Confirm ARP entry appears for pc_0_0 (ip neigh show).\n   - Ping pc_0_0 from leaf_router_0_0.\n\n3. From elsewhere on the fabric:\n   - Ping the corrected pc_0_0 IP to confirm reachability and that duplicate-IP condition is resolved.\n\nIf you want, I can provide exact commands for pc_0_0's OS, or perform follow-up checks (ARP, ping, packet capture) to validate the fix.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2617, "output_tokens": 264, "total_tokens": 2881, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2432}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
